"{\"uid\": \"techtimes.com-articles-302252-20240303-ai-powered-cameras-deployed-concerts-testing-olympics.htm\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"According toreports, the French police are testingAI-powered surveillance cameras this week to prepare for the cameras' intended deployment at the 2024 Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 167, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25, \"end\": 38, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0577899575335893e-27, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toreports\", \"from\": 10, \"to\": 19}, {\"ngram\": \"testingAI-powered surveillance cameras\", \"from\": 43, \"to\": 81}, {\"ngram\": \"the cameras' intended deployment\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 139}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 166}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Six AI-equipped cameras have been placed throughout the Accor Arena by Paris police for the first time in the country to track crowd movements and spot any unusual or dangerous activities.\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 240, \"end\": 245, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999998512976, \"rank\": 1.4862538407368052e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Six AI-equipped cameras\", \"from\": 169, \"to\": 192}, {\"ngram\": \"the Accor Arena\", \"from\": 221, \"to\": 236}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 246, \"to\": 252}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 271}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 286}, {\"ngram\": \"crowd movements\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"any unusual or dangerous activities\", \"from\": 321, \"to\": 356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The experiment's main goal is to get ready for the Paris Olympics, which takes place in five months and is predicted to provide a serious security issue for the police.\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The experiment's main goal\", \"from\": 359, \"to\": 385}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 424}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 438, \"to\": 443}, {\"ngram\": \"five months\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"a serious security issue\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 511}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 516, \"to\": 526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony is planned to be guarded by over 30,000 officers.\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 598, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 548}, {\"ngram\": \"over 30,000 officers\", \"from\": 577, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of the few new security initiatives being implemented for the 2024 Olympics is the use of AI-powered cameras.\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 713, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the few new security initiatives\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympics\", \"from\": 662, \"to\": 679}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 683, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"AI-powered cameras\", \"from\": 694, \"to\": 712}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According toreports, locals living close to Olympic venues would also have to apply for a QR code that would enable them to get by security obstacles.\", \"from\": 714, \"to\": 864, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"toreports\", \"from\": 724, \"to\": 733}, {\"ngram\": \"locals\", \"from\": 735, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic venues\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"a QR code\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 811}, {\"ngram\": \"security obstacles\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 863}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Residents of the prohibited zones would also be required to register any guests who might like to view the action from their houseboat, balcony, window, or rooftop.\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 1030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Residents\", \"from\": 866, \"to\": 875}, {\"ngram\": \"the prohibited zones\", \"from\": 879, \"to\": 899}, {\"ngram\": \"any guests\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 945}, {\"ngram\": \"the action\", \"from\": 969, \"to\": 979}, {\"ngram\": \"their houseboat\", \"from\": 985, \"to\": 1000}, {\"ngram\": \"window\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"rooftop\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Attendees of the Depeche Mode concerts on Sunday and Tuesday will be monitored by the security cameras.\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Depeche_Mode\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Depeche Mode\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q215380\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Depeche_Mode\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Depeche_Mode\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Attendees\", \"from\": 1032, \"to\": 1041}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1074, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"Tuesday\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1092}, {\"ngram\": \"the security cameras\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A bill authorizing the use of AI for the security of sporting and leisure events was passed by the French parliament in May of last year.\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1166, \"end\": 1168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"score\": 0.9999999999931788, \"rank\": 6.958327522422514e-12, \"text\": \"AI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Artificial_intelligence\"}, {\"begin\": 1235, \"end\": 1252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.313363880588519e-26, \"text\": \"French parliament\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q11204\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_Parliament\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A bill\", \"from\": 1136, \"to\": 1142}, {\"ngram\": \"the use\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1162}, {\"ngram\": \"the security\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1185}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting and leisure events\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1216}, {\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 1256, \"to\": 1259}, {\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 1263, \"to\": 1272}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However one of the grounds for the law was the turmoil of the 2022 Champions League Final between Real Madrid and Liverpool at the Stade de France, where fans were pepper sprayed by riot police and crushed in congested bottlenecks.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1506, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1342, \"end\": 1358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.705664504834371e-25, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 1389, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"score\": 0.9992642774914625, \"rank\": 0.0007362622861126766, \"text\": \"Liverpool\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liverpool_F.C.\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the grounds\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1301}, {\"ngram\": \"the law\", \"from\": 1306, \"to\": 1313}, {\"ngram\": \"the turmoil\", \"from\": 1318, \"to\": 1329}, {\"ngram\": \"Real Madrid\", \"from\": 1373, \"to\": 1384}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 1402, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1433}, {\"ngram\": \"